{"tid":1862771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【土瓜灣﹑何文田﹑黃埔 已出現確診個案】","createTime":"2020-02-04T20:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T23:48:52.000Z","uid":347229,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"026fff994c094ca7f55d46279231b35791b4174b","tid":1862771,"uid":347229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:58:27.000Z","msg":"推到記者問衛生署<br />\n<br />\n暫時 18 個案中，3單係幾日內出現於九龍城，而且地域相連什近，唔係一單係旺角，一單係黃埔，而係連住咁 黃埔﹑何文田﹑土瓜灣。<br />\n<br />\n想問衛生署:<br />\n1. 如何在社區大爆發前，「預先」加強力度打斷傳播鏈?<br />\n2. 會否安派人手進行消毒? 何種級數?<br />\n3. 三單個案有沒共通性? e.g.  交通工具 / 街市?  會否安排人員到懷疑地方採樣? <br />\n4. 如力度不足，令「黃何土」社區大爆發，會否建議當區市民在家辦公? (我知係廢問題，但有時D老闆係要理由)"},{"pid":"6510d08afbb8853bde0b09c41548249bf9c03172","tid":1862771,"uid":347229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T21:22:43.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f45282ea94ef10da8e398c1074620d5fc571384f","tid":1862771,"uid":61002,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T21:57:10.000Z","msg":"直接問九龍城區會唔會宣佈疫區"},{"pid":"af690d435ea35d183d78ce53723486812be599e0","tid":1862771,"uid":159414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T22:52:59.000Z","msg":"仲依靠衛生署？<br />\n全部都係呃飯食<br />\n無人真係把關做嘢"},{"pid":"f2c25896ee6f4fc4046aeb89660f2373b39b5b69","tid":1862771,"uid":246158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T23:04:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />九龍城區好多藍絲廢老<br />\n肯定係有人上完大陸之後播毒"},{"pid":"b74a825a6a24551cff7590710c4380497723466f","tid":1862771,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T23:48:52.000Z","msg":"消滅老鼠芬票倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}